ak up a nice skin)<br> . download nice skin<br> . tweak it a little bit<br> . use nice skin<br><br>I'd say give the new UI another 2-3 months before it's ready for prime time.  It's still very beta-quality -- major bugs are found every single day.  This means lots of code changes and chance for yet more bugs.  Also, even if you can do the mods yourself, there's literally an army of EQ addicts out there itching for the dubious fame of developing a popular skin.  Let them work for you!  Then, if you can and if you desire to do so, tweak one of theirs a little bit and voila!  You have a nice UI.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Mosushi, Lizard Master of the Fish<br><i>"I will gladly pay you Tuesday for Sushi today!"</i></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showPrevMessage?topicID=159.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showNextMessage?topicID=159.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=159.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.emailToFriend?topicID=159.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.threadControl?topicID=159.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43